*** Todo List App ***
This is a simple and user-friendly Todo List application built with React. It allows users to add and remove tasks efficiently, making it easier to manage daily goals and improve productivity.

🚀 Features
📌 Add new tasks quickly using the input field
❌ Remove tasks with a single click
✨ Clean and minimal UI design
💡 Built using React functional components and modern CSS

🛠️ Tech Stack
  * React
  * CSS (Vanilla)
